# paper Development Guidelines

Last updated: 2026-04-18

## Active Technologies
- PostgreSQL（业务数据、配置、日志、模板元数据）+ Redis（admin session、运行时缓存、队列/配置失效广播）

- TypeScript 5.x（前端 Vue 3、后端 NestJS 10） + Vue 3, Vite, Pinia, TailwindCSS, NestJS, Prisma, PostgreSQL, Redis, BullMQ

## Project Structure

```text
apps/
├── admin/
├── web/
└── server/
packages/
└── shared/
```

## Commands

- **Build/test/lint**: `pnpm --filter @ai-paper/server test; pnpm --filter @ai-paper/admin test; pnpm lint`

## Code Style

TypeScript 5.x（前端 Vue 3、后端 NestJS 10）: Follow standard conventions

